<plot>The Cars have always been on the cutting edge when it comes to music video. And the Heartbeat City video cassette, with songs from their off the band's most successful albums, is no exception. Andy Warhol's direction of Heartbeat City brings forth the fun of Disco into the new avenues of the early to mid 80's.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?095367</url></doc>
